name: Ranni Elden Ring | Character LoRA
description:
Ranni Elden Ring | Character LoRA


Weight can go from 0.7 up to 1.0. I recommend 0.9. Works with almost every Style, Concept and Photorealistic Models.

SD doesn't really want to generate images with extra arms and blue skin, so take that in considerration.

V2:

Trigger Word:

Ranni

Helping Prompt:

cracked skin, blue skin, colored skin, extra arms, joints, doll joints, dress

V1:

Trigger Word:

Ranni

Witchform Prompt:

(cracked skin, blue skin, colored skin, 4 arms, extra arms:1.3), joints, doll joints

Helping Prompt:
1girl, solo, long hair, one eye closed, blue eyes, blue hair, wavy hair

Outfit Prompt:

hat, dress, holding, wide sleeves, white dress, witch hat, white headwear, cloak, witch, fur cloak

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Download LoRA

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA and use the triggerword

  • Make sure to change the weight if needed (by default it's :1)

  • Have Fun!
